{"tid":2057911,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"城大是世界上首間因應疫情而率先推行網上教學的大學","createTime":"2020-06-09T17:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T03:03:43.000Z","uid":30836,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8d4778898b5ad020d146cfafd62a0769cddfd501","tid":2057911,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:47:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">2019/20 下學期順利完成</div></strong><br />\n因應疫情發展，大學率先於2月7日實施CityU-Learning，按原定時間表、全校性、實時、為研究生及本科生網上授課。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，城大是香港的八大中，甚至是世界上首間因應疫情而率先推行網上教學的大學。</span></strong><br />\n <br />\n根據我們於2月及3月進行先導及全校性問卷調查結果顯示，網上教學<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行之有效</span></strong>。<br />\n <br />\n在3 月 30 日至 5 月 10 日進行的2019/20下學期期末全校性教與學問卷，共收到39,451份問卷，其中第10條 「整體而言，我認為老師提供了有價值的學習體驗。」的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">總平均分為5.76</span></strong>（7分為非常認同、1分為非常不認同）。教與學問卷結果今日已發放予相關人員。<br />\n <br />\n調查結果反映全校師生的共同努力和積極進取。 我們衷心感謝各學術和行政部門的教職員及學生的合作和大力支持。<br />\n <br />\n任廣禹<br />\n學務副校長<br />\n2020年6月9日"},{"pid":"ac373795f00389b41015a4121400825f6ffee76e","tid":2057911,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:47:43.000Z","msg":"吾城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b18d260d014b93ee245884ab0860991ba91939","tid":2057911,"uid":192409,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:48:50.000Z","msg":"咁都有得J"},{"pid":"77768a98b029e3904dc20dd8168cd44d3992773d","tid":2057911,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"全球第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ec73f590d942348c09176d9b30bc09b1e658a2","tid":2057911,"uid":199479,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T17:50:54.000Z","msg":"既然online learning咁方便 不如以後全部都